ARGS: {"account_id": "hubspot_001", "name": "Yamini Rangan", "title": "President, CEO and Board Member", "email": "yamini.rangan@hubspot.com"}

THOUGHT: Contact saved successfully. Now I need to draft a personalized email using the Spring 2026 Spotlight signal and the new product launches (AEO, Smart Deal). I'll reference their recent innovations and growth focus.
ACTION: draft_email
ARGS: {"contact_name": "Yamini Rangan", "title": "President, CEO and Board Member", "company": "HubSpot", "signal": "Spring 2026 Spotlight launch with new AEO and Smart Deal products targeting go-to-market teams; Q4 2025 financial results pending", "sender_context": "GTM Prospect Agent researching companies with strong product innovation signals in the agentic AI and revenue intelligence space"}
